FBIS3-18276 "drweu040_l_94003" FBIS-WEU-94-040 Document Type:Daily Report 1 Mar 1994 SPAIN Hijackers Surrender LD2802173894 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network in Spanish 1710 GMT 28 Feb 94 LD2802173894 Madrid RNE-1 Radio Network Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Excerpts] We now have a flash from Alicante. [passage omitted] It seems that the three hijackers have just given themselves up to the Spanish police. [passage omitted] Concha Flores reports: [Flores] A few minutes ago, the spokesman for the Alicante Civil Government, Mariano Soriano, told us that at 1805 the three hijackers of this Air Algerie plane gave themselves up to the Spanish security forces who had cordoned off the plane. It seems that negotiations that were taking place from the runway were effective and as we said the news has been officially confirmed by the civil government that the three hijackers have given themselves up. [passage omitted]
